In order to get your code working I would suggest the following:

Get rid of the `move()` method and its `for` loop. Instead, utilize a counter within a Swing Timer&#39;s **ActionPerformed** event to carry out the similar thing. Below is your code quickly modified to work with a Swing Timer. Read the comments in code:

